{"metadata":{"role":"symbol","roleHeading":"Instance Property","title":"zoomLevel","symbolKind":"property","fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"zoomLevel"}],"externalID":"c:objc(cs)MLNMapView(py)zoomLevel","navigatorTitle":[{"text":"zoomLevel","kind":"identifier"}],"remoteSource":{"url":"https:\/\/github.com\/maplibre\/maplibre-native\/blob\/main\/platform\/ios\/src\/MLNMapView.h#L1026","fileName":"MLNMapView.h"},"modules":[{"name":"MapLibre"}]},"sections":[],"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"The zoom level of the receiver."}],"primaryContentSections":[{"declarations":[{"tokens":[{"text":"@property","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" (","kind":"text"},{"text":"nonatomic","kind":"keyword"},{"text":") ","kind":"text"},{"text":"double","preciseIdentifier":"c:d","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"text":"zoomLevel","kind":"identifier"},{"kind":"text","text":";"}],"platforms":["iOS","iPadOS","Mac Catalyst"],"languages":["occ"]}],"kind":"declarations"},{"content":[{"text":"Discussion","type":"heading","anchor":"discussion","level":2},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"In addition to affecting the visual size and detail of features on the map,"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"the zoom level affects the size of the vector tiles that are loaded. At zoom","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"level 0, each tile covers the entire world map; at zoom level 1, it covers ¼","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"of the world; at zoom level 2, "},{"type":"text","text":"1"},{"type":"text","text":"⁄"},{"type":"text","text":"16"},{"type":"text","text":" of the world, and"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"so on."}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Changing the value of this property updates the map view immediately. If you"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"want to animate the change, use the "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"-setZoomLevel:animated:"},{"type":"text","text":" method instead."}]}],"kind":"content"}],"schemaVersion":{"major":0,"patch":0,"minor":3},"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre","doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapView"]]},"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapView\/zoomLevel","interfaceLanguage":"occ"},"kind":"symbol","variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"occ"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnmapview\/zoomlevel"]}],"references":{"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNMapView/zoomLevel":{"title":"zoomLevel","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnmapview\/zoomlevel","abstract":[{"text":"The zoom level of the receiver.","type":"text"}],"kind":"symbol","type":"topic","fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"zoomLevel"}],"role":"symbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapView\/zoomLevel"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNMapView":{"kind":"symbol","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnmapview","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"An interactive, customizable map view with an interface similar to the one"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"provided by Apple’s MapKit."}],"title":"MLNMapView","type":"topic","fragments":[{"text":"MLNMapView","kind":"identifier"}],"role":"symbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapView"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre":{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre","role":"collection","kind":"symbol","type":"topic","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre","title":"MapLibre","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Powerful, free and open-source mapping toolkit with full control over data sources and styling."}]}}}